"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-03-Olympic-spirit-unshaken-Debunking-claims-of-Chinese-disinterest-1vKku3ePNJK-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  Rumor has it that Chinese netizens are losing interest in the Paris Olympics due to \\\"social, economic and political\\\" issues. But is this the truth? A closer look at social media trends and public engagement tells a different story. Despite current challenges, the enthusiasm and support for the Olympics among Chinese netizens remain strong.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"